{
  "title": "How can I delegate a report to my collage?",
  "slug": "how-can-i-delegate-a-report-to-my-collage",
  "categorySlug": "organisational-roll-out",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">How can I delegate a report to my collage?</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">If you need to substitut or delegate a report to another user, this is what you need to do.</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><p>The prerequisite for this is that you must have DMCS admin access.</p>\n<p>Then you go to the DMCS user list:</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Azure_users\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"360\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Azure_users.png?width=688&amp;height=360&amp;name=Azure_users.png\" width=\"688\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Azure_users.png?width=344&amp;height=180&amp;name=Azure_users.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Azure_users.png?width=688&amp;height=360&amp;name=Azure_users.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Azure_users.png?width=1032&amp;height=540&amp;name=Azure_users.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Azure_users.png?width=1376&amp;height=720&amp;name=Azure_users.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Azure_users.png?width=1720&amp;height=900&amp;name=Azure_users.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Azure_users.png?width=2064&amp;height=1080&amp;name=Azure_users.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p>On the 'Azure user' tab, it is visible which other accounts a particular user has access to read. This typically includes shared mailboxes, allowing the user to access and manage emails and other communication within those shared accounts. Having this insight can be helpful for administrators to understand the extent of a user's access and permissions within the DMCS system.</p>\n<p>By clicking on the three small dots, you can easily add another email account that you require access to. This feature allows you to seamlessly expand your access to additional accounts within the DMCS system, providing you with a comprehensive view of all relevant information and communication.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Delegated access\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"333\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Delegated%20access.png?width=688&amp;height=333&amp;name=Delegated%20access.png\" width=\"688\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Delegated%20access.png?width=344&amp;height=167&amp;name=Delegated%20access.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Delegated%20access.png?width=688&amp;height=333&amp;name=Delegated%20access.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Delegated%20access.png?width=1032&amp;height=500&amp;name=Delegated%20access.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Delegated%20access.png?width=1376&amp;height=666&amp;name=Delegated%20access.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Delegated%20access.png?width=1720&amp;height=833&amp;name=Delegated%20access.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Delegated%20access.png?width=2064&amp;height=999&amp;name=Delegated%20access.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p>The result will be that your personal report will be enriched with the accounts you add, providing you with a more comprehensive overview of all the relevant information and communication within the DMCS system.</p>\n<p>This expanded access allows you to effectively manage and monitor a wider range of accounts, enabling you to stay informed and in control of all necessary data and communication channels.</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
  "sourceUrl": "https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/how-can-i-delegate-a-report-to-my-collage"
}